data.title: You're Not Alone
data.meta_description:
You're Not Alone by Ok Go & Bonerama, released 07 November 2006

1. Rock 'N' Roll Suicide
2. A Million Ways
3. Oh Lately It's So Quiet
4. It's A Disaster
5. I Shall Be Released

Ok Go and Bonerama join forces for this iTunes only benefit release. In the wake of Hurricane Katrina, Damian Kulash and Ok Go collided with Bonerama to record 5 tunes in New Orleans and the bands joined forces on shows in New Orleans and Washington DC in addition to Damian and Bonerama performing "A Million Ways" on The Late Show with David Letterman.

To buy this album on iTunes, please click here: http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/youre-not-alone-ep/id273201763
data.text:
Even in a city that doesn’t play by the rules, New Orleans’ Bonerama is something different. They can evoke vintage funk, classic rock and free improvisation in the same set; maybe even the same song. Bonerama has been repeatedly recognized by Rolling Stone, hailed as “the ultimate in brass balls” (David Fricke - 2005).

You don't have to be afraid anymore... ... more
